articles.headline: Sources: Justice Fitzpatrick, brother of Minkah, picks Georgia
articles.description: Four-star cornerback Justice Fitzpatrick, the younger brother of Minkah, has committed to Georgia, sources told ESPN, picking the Bulldogs over Florida, Miami, Ohio State and Texas.

articles.headline: Jeff Darlington: Belichick's NFL return unlikely for now

images.name: Jeff Darlington: Belichick's NFL return unlikely for now
images.caption: Jeff Darlington explains why there's no expectation that Bill Belichick will return to the NFL at this time, despite the fact that the buyout in his contract recently dropped from $10 million to $1 million.
